{
  "stem": "7684.10",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And Holland was not built in all these years, so you couldn't get a store.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So there was a family what had a store, and they didn't have a license to open it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I didn't want to start a business with them, but Chaim was desperate to get out of that hotel.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We were both desperate to get out of the hotel, but did very well, and we made very money.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "When it was a kettle market.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And was every Friday we made a lot of money.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But we didn't get along, so what has-- all the money has nothing to do with it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we get the license.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was also in Holland.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You have to have a license.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the license was of the name for my father and mother, and you could write it over once.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And Chaim say, your brother is the oldest from the family, and he's the only one that came back.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He deserves it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So he gave the license to my brother for that hotel.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And my sister-in-law was not a house wife, so the hotel went down, down, down.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then the people where we want to go to business with were not very nice people.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But Chaim was so desperate, so we started a business with these people, textile store.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we did very well.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We bought-- we built a house.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Also from the money-- we got a little bit money from the German-- from the Dutch government, because what we went through.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they stole-- the Germans stole.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we bought-- we build a house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "A little house.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we did well, and everything was fine.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then the people that we took the business with-- and then came the Korean War.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the business went debt.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
